<html>

<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
    <meta https-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
    <meta name="HandheldFriendly" content="true">
    <title>SignUp</title>
    <style>
        @media screen and (max-width:768px) {
            .email-template-container {
                max-width: 85% !important;
            }
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 670px),
        screen and (max-device-width: 670px) {
            .email-template-container {
                width: 100% !important;
                max-width: 100% !important;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (max-width:575px) {
            .email-template-container .email-content {
                margin: 0px !important;
            }

            .email-template-container {
                padding: 0px !important;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (max-width:475px) {
            .content-head {
                padding: 0px 0px !important;
            }

            .email-header {
                margin-bottom: 15px !important;
            }

            .email-content {
                padding: 15px !important;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (max-width:425px) {
            .email-template-container .verify-link {
                padding: 12px 35px !important;
            }

            .social-icons {
                padding: 15px 0px !important;
            }

            .email-content .content-body {
                padding: 15px 0px !important;
            }

            .email-content .content-footer {
                padding: 15px 0px 0px !important;
            }
        }

        @media screen and (max-width:376px) {
            .email-template-container .content-head h2 {
                font-size: 25px !important;
            }

            .email-content .social-icons a {
                margin: 0px 10px !important;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <table class="email-template-container"
        style="padding: 0px; width: 570px; max-width: 100%; max-height: inherit; margin: auto;  font-family: Roboto Verdana, Geneva, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size:15px; margin:0 auto"
        width="638">
        <tr>
            <td>
                <div class="email-content"
                    style="padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #C4C4C4; box-sizing: border-box; background: #FFFFFF;">
                    <table>
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <div class="content-head" style="padding: 10px 0px;">
                                    <h2
                                        style="font-style: normal; font-weight: 500; font-size: 28px; line-height: 35px; text-align: center; color: #0D2541; margin: 10px 0px; line-height:45px">
                                        Thank you for registering with iHostYoutPet.</h2>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <div class="content-body" style="padding: 30px 0px;">
                                    <p
                                        style="margin: 10px 0px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 20px; color: #3C3C4C;">
                                        <b style="line-height: 18px;">Hi </b><b style="line-height: 18px;">
                                            <%=name%>,
                                        </b>
                                    </p>
                                    <p
                                        style="margin: 10px 0px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; color: #3C3C4C; ">
                                        Welcome to iHostYourPet. We’re so excited you have chosen us for your pet
                                        boarding needs. Your account informations are -</p>
                                    <p
                                        style="margin: 10px 0px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; color: #3C3C4C; ">
                                        Email:<b>
                                            <%=email%>
                                        </b></p>
                                    <p
                                        style="margin: 10px 0px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; color: #3C3C4C; ">
                                        Password - <b>
                                            <%=password%>
                                        </b></p>

                                    <p
                                        style="margin: 10px 0px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; color: #3C3C4C; ">
                                        To help you get started, we recommend you to add the following details in My Profile section of your dashboard - 
                                        <ol>
                                            <li>Pet details </li>
                                             <li>Schedule</li>    
                                               
                                        </ol>
                                       <p  style="margin: 10px 0px; font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; color: #3C3C4C; ">
                                        Next, please go to the Members page and search for hosts as per your date and zip code. Request a booking to your preferred host and await their response. Once the host accepts your request, you can now board your pets to the host’s address.
                                       </p>  
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </td>
                        </tr>

                    </table>
                    <table class="content-footer" style="padding: 10px 0px;">
                        <tr>
                            <td> <span
                                    style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; color: #88939C;">
                                    If you need any support, send us an email at  <a
                                        href="mailto:ihostyourpet@gmail.com" style="text-decoration: none;"> <span
                                            class="link-text"
                                            style="font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px; color: #00619D;">ihostyourpet@gmail.com
                                        </span> 
                                    </a>
                                    and we will be happy to help.   
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
</body>

</html>